1. *Prihvatio* sam pozivnicu za venčanje. (I accepted the wedding invitation.)
2. Oni *su prihvatili* našu ponudu. (They accepted our offer.)
3. Ti nisi *prihvatio* moj savet. (You didn't accept my advice.)
4. *Prihvati* činjenice i kreni dalje. (Accept the facts and move on.)
5. Kada *sam prihvatio* posao, osetio sam olakšanje. (When I accepted the job, I felt relieved.)
6. Da li ćeš *prihvatiti* izvinjenje? (Will you accept the apology?)
7. *Prihvatanje* novih izazova može biti uzbudljivo. (Accepting new challenges can be exciting.)
8. Njihov šef nije *prihvatio* njihovu ostavku. (Their boss didn't accept their resignation.)
9. Ona *je prihvatila* njegovu ponudu za izlazak. (She accepted his offer to go out.)
10. Na kraju, *prihvatio sam* da sam pogrešio. (In the end, I accepted that I was wrong.)